        <mxCell id="Luutr2t2g2QciU9risVp-148" parent="fdHg4GswKJxgz0AEHUep-218" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;Use rejection sampling to find x. Set the following upper and lower bounds on x:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Lower bound is the higher of either 0 or f-1.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- Upper bound is f&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
